"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-07-13-Chinese-discus-thrower-Feng-Bin-to-dance-again-at-2024-Olympic-Games-1vcfPXPv33y-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports Scene  Copied  Feng Bin, 30, of China, has no other goal than competing for the women's discus throw gold medal at the 2024 Summer Olympic Games in Paris.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 227, \"end\": 235, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feng_Bin\", \"score\": 0.9999960498510775, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Feng Bin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feng_Bin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feng_Bin\"}, {\"begin\": 244, \"end\": 249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9362629525151341, \"rank\": 0.047608149114202705, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 360, \"end\": 365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999942758677, \"rank\": 5.724072391957586e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back in 2016, Feng finished within the top in her Olympic debut in Rio de Janeiro.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 450, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 449, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"score\": 0.9999999993926849, \"rank\": 6.072534997361074e-10, \"text\": \"Rio de Janeiro\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rio_de_Janeiro\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, five years later, she failed to make the final at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 451, \"to\": 529, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The setback did not hurt her confidence because her excellent performances in 2022 and 2023 gave her every reason to continue to believe in herself.\", \"from\": 530, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In July 20, 2022, Feng threw personal-best 69.12 meters at the World Athletics Championships in Eugene, Oregon, beating Sandra Perkovic of Croatia and Valarie Allman of the U.S. to win the gold.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 874, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 743, \"end\": 772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"score\": 0.9884951462479101, \"rank\": 0.004456284512622916, \"text\": \"World Athletics Championships\", \"types\": [\"Q1656682\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Athletics_Championships\"}, {\"begin\": 784, \"end\": 790, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"score\": 0.8518661085238248, \"rank\": 0.170729574847286, \"text\": \"Oregon\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Oregon\"}, {\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 806, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\", \"score\": 0.9999603806702178, \"rank\": 3.809984669451018e-05, \"text\": \"Sandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10833314\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Klemenschits\"}, {\"begin\": 819, \"end\": 826, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_men's_national_handball_team\", \"score\": 0.9989581610033453, \"rank\": 0.0010267151583422606, \"text\": \"Croatia\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_men's_national_handball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Croatia_men's_national_handball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 831, \"end\": 845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valarie_Allman\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Valarie Allman\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valarie_Allman\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Valarie_Allman\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her victory ended Chinese athletes' 11-year title drought in the women's discus throw event at the World Championships.\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 994, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 893, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.5562315145226584, \"rank\": 0.7973464154642222, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I felt such a relief at that moment because I proved I could do it,\\\" Feng told China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 996, \"to\": 1100, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1076, \"end\": 1093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 1095, \"end\": 1098, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9891150819015513, \"rank\": 0.011004670161830678, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Many did not think I could win before the final, but I won it in the end.\", \"from\": 1101, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I proved myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1193, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One year later in August 2023, Feng threw 68.2 meters in her final attempt at the World Championships in Budapest, Hungary to bring home a bronze medal.\", \"from\": 1195, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1300, \"end\": 1308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"score\": 0.9999694355118078, \"rank\": 3.056523712717521e-05, \"text\": \"Budapest\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Budapest\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was the second-best performance of her career and led to her qualification for the 2024 Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1348, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Feng continued to maintain a superb form in 2024.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1504, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She threw over 67 meters in six of the competitions she has participated in this season.\", \"from\": 1505, \"to\": 1593, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She is currently third in the world behind Yaime Perez of Cuba and Allman.\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1668, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1637, \"end\": 1648, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaime_P\\u00e9rez\", \"score\": 0.9999999999058673, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yaime Perez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaime_P\\u00e9rez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Yaime_P\\u00e9rez\"}, {\"begin\": 1652, \"end\": 1656, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\", \"score\": 0.8852679083205145, \"rank\": 0.11252214880027171, \"text\": \"Cuba\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cuba_national_baseball_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though discus throw looks like and is indeed a sport about power, but it also feels like a ballet to Feng.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1776, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why she has been working hard on improving her flexibility and coordination, which can even match some short-distance hurdling athletes.\", \"from\": 1777, \"to\": 1920, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am in a good form now,\\\" Feng said.\", \"from\": 1922, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just focus on training and improving my performance.\", \"from\": 1960, \"to\": 2015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As long as I can maintain regular practice, I will not perform badly in Paris.\", \"from\": 2016, \"to\": 2094, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2088, \"end\": 2093, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999942758677, \"rank\": 5.724072391957586e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My goal of the year is definitely to win the gold at the 2024 Olympics.\\\"\", \"from\": 2095, \"to\": 2167, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2429, \"entities\": []}]}"